txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Heavy sword sheaths from the Orcs, Angmarim, and Earth-kin north and east of Esteldín. Deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
'We can make use of these, thank you.'
'Worked leather is helpful to us here. If we can get some in any form from the enemies to the east, we will be better prepared for the future.'
Rangers of Esteldín Task: Heavy Sword Sheaths
Ferrif, a Ranger, has asked for a collection of heavy sword sheaths to be delivered to him at the Ranger's home at Esteldín.
Deliver the heavy sword sheaths to Ferrif in Esteldín

You have accepted a task to collect heavy sword sheaths from the Orcs, Angmarim, and Earth-kin in the area surrounding Esteldín to the east and north. Once collected, you are to deliver the items to Ferrif within Esteldín.
Wanted: Heavy sword sheaths from the Orcs, Angmarim, and Earth-kin north and east of Esteldín.
